data.description: WELCOME TO THE LOVELY AGE RESTRICTED COMMUNITY OF SOLERA.  HOUSE IS ON A CORNER LOT WITH 2 BEDROOMS AND A DEN. ENTRY HALLWAY TO  THE WHITNEY MODEL WHICH OFFERS  AN OPEN FLOOR PLAN WITH THE LIVING ROOM, DINING AREA, AND KITCHEN ALL OPEN TO EACH OTHER. GLASS SLIDING DOOR OPENS TO PATIO AND YARD. THE KITCHEN HAS CORIAN COUNTERS, A STAINLESS STEEL REFRIGERATOR NEWER  DISHWASHER .. CERAMIC TILE FLOORS IN ALL WET AREAS. LARGE PRIMARY BEDROOM WITH OVERSIZED CLOSET. THE PRIMARY BEDROOM IS SEPARATE FROM THE GUEST BEDROOM. NEWER WATER HEATER. BLINDS IN ALL WINDOWS. THE YARD HAS A COVERED PATIO READY FOR RELAXING OR DINING WITH VERY LITTLE MAINTENANCE. SID/LID ARE PAID IN FULL
